<H3>SPECIAL REPORT THE MFJ--FRONT PAGE NEWS</H3>
<UL>
<A HREF = "#1"><LI>RHCs PLAN 1990 GRASSROOTS EFFORT TO RELAX MFJ RULES</A>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp<NOBR>(1744 words)</NOBR></LI>
