<H3>NETWORKS</H3>
<UL>
<A HREF = "#2"><A HREF = "#2"><LI>CONGRESS, BUREAUCRACY HAVE HANDS-ON EXPERIENCE WITH NEW PHONE&nbsp;SYSTEMS</A>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp<NOBR>(740 words)</NOBR></LI>
</UL>
<BR>
