FRANCE TELECOM INCREASING INVESTMENT

France Telecom is to make its mobile network one of its top priorities
according to new chief executive Michel Bon.  He says it will increase
investment in its GSM network from this year with a view to being able
to support five million subscribers by the year 2000.





