market trials in Idaho Falls and Pocatello, Idaho, and Yakima, Wash.,
are completed.  Tele-Go operates as a cordless phone in a user's
residence and as a cellular phone on the cellular network when the
handset is away from the enhanced cordless base station installed in
the user's residence.  (Byron Cheatham, USC, 312/399-4157; Joann
Riner, GTE, 770/804-3742.)



