<H3>CYBERGUIDE</H3>
<UL>
<A HREF = "#58"><LI>CyberGuide: COMPUTERWARE</A>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp<NOBR>(692 words)</NOBR></LI>
<A HREF = "#59"><LI>CyberGuide: Dollars & Sense</A>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp<NOBR>(397 words)</NOBR></LI>
