The Russian government and Italian state telecommunications holding
company Stet failed to reach agreement about Stet's purchase of a 25-
per-cent stake in Russian regional telecommunications holding company
Svyazinvest (Telecom Markets, 282/17).  A new tender will have to be
launched next year.





