NEW PRESIDENT FOR AT&T

AT&T chairman Robert Allen has announced the selection of Alex Mandl as
president and chief operating officer of the new AT&T and member of the
company's board of directors.  Mandl, who has headed the company's long-
distance services business since 1993, will report to Allen.





